## Task Format
The task requires the assistant to analyze the dimensions of iris petals and sepals in centimeters and predict the corresponding species of iris.

## Input Format
The inputs will consist of four numerical values:

* petal_length (cm)
* petal_width (cm)
* sepal_length (cm)
