### flavonoids (float): The flavonoid content of the wine in grams per liter.
### nonflavanoid_phenols (float): The nonflavanoid phenol content of the wine in grams per liter.
### proanthocyanins (float): The proanthocyanin content of the wine in grams per liter.
### color_intensity (float): The color intensity of the wine in degrees.
### proline (float): The proline content of the wine in milligrams per gram.
### volatile_acidity (float): The volatile acidity of the wine in milligrams per liter.
### nonflavanoid_phenol_acidity (float): The nonflavanoid phenol acidity of the wine in milligrams per liter.
### residual_sugar (float): The residual sugar content of the wine in grams per liter.
### chlorides (float): The chloride content of the wine in milligrams per liter.
### free_sulfur_dioxide (float): The free sulfur dioxide content of the wine in milligrams per liter.
### total_sulfur_dioxide (float): The total sulfur dioxide content of the wine in milligrams per liter.
### density (float): The density of the wine in grams per milliliter.
### sulphates (float): The sulfate content of the wine in milligrams per liter.
### alcohol (float): The alcohol content of the wine in degrees.
### quality (float): The quality of the wine (target variable).

